description: Modifies an existing DB subnet group. DB subnet groups must contain at least one subnet in at least two AZs in the Amazon Web Services Region.

parameters.name: DBSubnetGroupName
parameters.description: The name for the DB subnet group. This value is stored as a lowercase string. You can't modify the default subnet group. Constraints: Must match the name of an existing DBSubnetGroup. Must not be default. Example: mydbsubnetgroup.

parameters.name: SubnetIds
parameters.description: The EC2 subnet IDs for the DB subnet group. (string) ---
